": "of Hell. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Intenseness,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "vehemence,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of heat; (TA;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faworapN", "text_ar": "فَوْرَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faworu Al$~afaqi", "text_ar": "فَوْرُ الشَّفَقِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The remains of the redness in the western horizon after sunset:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vaworuhu", "text_ar": "ثَوْرُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faworapN", "text_ar": "فَوْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]       -A2-  And"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A time:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) [or rather] the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "present time in which is no delaying."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) Thus in the saying,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Al$~ufoEapu", "text_ar": "الشُّفْعَةُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EalaY Alfawori", "text_ar": "عَلَى الفَوْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The right of pre-emption is to be had"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the present time in which is no delaying."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) ―         -b2-  And hence,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A state in which is no delay."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaA='a fulaAnN fiY HaAjatihi vum~a rajaEa", "text_ar": "جَا=ءَ فُلَانٌ فِى حَاجَتِهِ ثُمَّ رَجَعَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino faworihi", "text_ar": "مِنْ فَوْرِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Such a one came for the object of his want,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "then returned immediately,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "at once:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or, as some say,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with the same motion with which he came, not ceasing from motion after it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "properly,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "conjoining what was before the coming with what was after it, without tarrying."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^atawoA mino faworihimo", "text_ar": "اَتَوْا مِنْ فَوْرِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino wajohihimo", "text_ar": "مِنْ وَجْهِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e., app.,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They came in a headlong manner;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "like the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maDaY EalaY wajohihi", "text_ar": "مَضَى عَلَى وَجْهِهِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]; (M, K, TA; but the M has"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jaAw^uwA", "text_ar": "جَاوُوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "instead of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^atawoA", "text_ar": "اَتَوْا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ";) and this is said by Zj to be the meaning of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino faworihimo", "text_ar": "مِنْ فَوْرِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the Kur iii. 121: (M, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qabola A^ano yasokunuwA", "text_ar": "قَبْلَ اَنْ يَسْكُنُوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "before their resting,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ceasing from motion"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (K, TA:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino faworihimo", "text_ar": "مِنْ فَوْرِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the Kur ubi suprà means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the commencement of their procedure:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "at, their instant of time;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Ksh, Bd;) i. e. ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "at, the same instant,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "immediately:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^atayotu fulaAnFA", "text_ar": "اَتَيْتُ فُلَانًا"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mino faworiY", "text_ar": "مِنْ فَوْرِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qabola A^ano A^asokuna", "text_ar": "قَبْلَ اَنْ اَسْكُنَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[i. e."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I came to such a one before my resting,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ceasing from motion"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S, O.) And you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faEalotuhu mino faworiY", "text_ar": "فَعَلْتُهُ مِنْ فَوْرِى"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I did it at once,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "instantly."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(T, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["TA", "M", "K", "O", "Bd"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}